            <h6>Question 2</h6>
            <h5>Should the supreme court be reformed to include more seats and term limits on judges?</h5>
            <select class="form-control" id="exampleFormControlSelect1">
                <option value = "1">Yes, add more seats and term limits on judges</option>
                <option value = "2">Yes, but only to impose term limits</option>
