            </select>

            <br><br>
            <h6>Question 7</h6>
            <h5>Do you support a single-payer healthcare system (Medicare for all)?</h5>
            <select class="form-control" id="exampleFormControlSelect1">
                <option value = "1">Yes, private companies should not be able to profit off healtcare </option>
                <option value = "2">Yes, this system guarentees healthcare for all</option>
                <option value = "3">Yes, but still allow people to use private insurance</option>
                <option value = "4">No, this system is too expensive</option>
                <option value = "5">No, the government should not be involved in healthcare
