            </select>

            <br><br>
            <h6>Question 8</h6>
            <h5>Should cities open drug "safe havens" where people who are addicted to illegal drugs can use them under the supervision of medical professionals?</h5>
            <select class="form-control" id="exampleFormControlSelect1">
                <option value = "1">Yes, drug abuse should be treated as a health issue, not a criminal issue.</option>
                <!-- <option value = "2">2</option>
                <option value = "3">3</option> -->
