            <br><br>
            <h6>Question 12</h6>
            <h5>Should disposable products (such as plastic cups, plates, and cutlery) that contain less than 50% of biodegradable material be banned?</h5>
            <select class="form-control" id="exampleFormControlSelect1">
                <option value = "1">Yes, anything that contains less than 75%	</option>
                <option value = "2">Yes, anything less than 50%</option>
